# Project Initiation & SRS Documentation

This directory contains the Software Requirements Specification (SRS) and initial project planning documents for the **Hackathon Team Management System**.

---

## ğŸ¯ Project Selection

The project for the SEAD Hackathon was selected after brainstorming multiple problem statements and evaluating them based on several key factors:
* **Feasibility**: Assessment of technical requirements and project timeline.
* **Innovation**: Focusing on a unique solution for hackathon organization.
* **Real-world Applicability**: Solving the common struggle of team coordination during high-pressure events.
* **Alignment**: Meeting the core objectives of software engineering principles.

The selection was finalized through mutual discussion and agreement among all team members to ensure a unified vision and commitment.

